<D>__{hey doc!}
<A>__{camera pans to show a group of poker players seated around a table. this consists of a well dressed, powerful looking man of about 45 (judge garvey), with a smooth face and an impressive manner; a flashily dressed young man with a weak face (clint harolday); a tough looking cowboy of about 35 (ab jenkins); a pleasant faced storekeeper of about 50 (pap fossler); and a little man with a weather beaten face and intensely blue eyes (doc riding). watching the game are sam haynes and shorty davis, the former a townsman and the latter a cowboy. as they all look toward the door, cap's voice continues.}
